ad_text:
I always try to choose pieces that I know will last more than one season. Nothing too trendy, never something that isn’t true to my personal style. I mostly avoid fast fashion because often the quality isn’t meant to last. It’s fun to experiment, but if you’re trying too hard, it always shows… 
Mix it up with sculptural elements & interesting detail, but keep it timeless.♟️ 

*SIMILAR linked in my LTK

@zara off-shoulder cut out top & balloon pant
@megajewelry earrings from @modaoperandi @jamiek

